# Claude Code Test Runner - Environment Configuration
# For detailed configuration, see: docker-compose/.env.example

# ============================================================================
# Quick Setup Instructions
# ============================================================================
# 1. Copy docker-compose/.env.example to docker-compose/.env
# 2. Update with your actual values
# 3. Run: docker compose up -d
# 4. Access: http://localhost:8013

# ============================================================================
# Database Configuration
# ============================================================================
POSTGRES_DB=cc_test_db
POSTGRES_USER=cc_test_user
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=your_secure_password_here

# ============================================================================
# Redis Configuration
# ============================================================================
REDIS_PASSWORD=your_redis_password_here

# ============================================================================
# Security Configuration
# ============================================================================
SECRET_KEY=your-secret-key-change-in-production-12345678

# ============================================================================
# AI Services Configuration (Optional)
# ============================================================================
# For AI-powered test execution, configure these in docker-compose/.env:
#
# Option 1: Anthropic Claude
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.anthropic.com
#
# Option 2: GLM (智谱AI) - Recommended for Chinese
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-glm-api-key-here
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/anthropic
#
# Get API keys:
# - Claude: https://console.anthropic.com/
# - GLM: https://open.bigmodel.cn/

# ============================================================================
# Service Ports
# ============================================================================
# Test Case Service: http://localhost:8011
# Scheduler Service: http://localhost:8012
# Dashboard Service: http://localhost:8013

# ============================================================================
# Documentation
# ============================================================================
# See docker-compose/.env.example for complete configuration options
# Quick config guide: docker-compose/QUICK_CONFIG.md
# GLM integration: docker-compose/GLM_INTEGRATION.md